<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->
    <title>Account Setup</title>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
    <script src="bootstrap-3.3.6-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="bootstrap-3.3.6-dist/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="bootstrap-3.3.6-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/common.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/setup.css">

    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
      <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
      <![endif]-->

      <link rel="stylesheet" href="jquery-ui-1.11.4.custom/jquery-ui.min.css">
      <script src="jquery-ui-1.11.4.custom/external/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
      <script src="jquery-ui-1.11.4.custom/jquery-ui.js"></script>
      <script src="jquery-ui-1.11.4.custom/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>

      <script>
        $(function() {
          $( "#date" ).datepicker();
        });
      </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid" id="setup">
      <!-- First section -->
      <div class="setup1">
        <h1>Welcome to Piggy!</h1>
        <h4>Piggy will help you save money for the things that matter to you. Based on your saving goal, this guide will calculate your daily spending budget. Stick to your budget, and you'll easily reach your goal!</h4>
        <hr>
        <h3>Step 1: Tell us about your monthly financial situation.</h3>
        <form>
          <p>What is your income per month?</p>
            <input type="number" id="monthlyIncome" name="monthlyIncome" placeholder="$ Enter an amount">
            <br><br> <!-- add margins in css later and remove <br> -->
          <p>How much goes towards necessities (rent, utilities, groceries, insurance, fees, etc.)?</p>
            <input type="number" id="necessities" name="necessities" placeholder="$ Enter an amount">
            <br><br> <!-- add margins in css later and remove <br> -->
          <p>How much did you spend this month so far EXCLUDING necessities?</p>
            <input type="number" id="spentSoFar" name="spentSoFar" placeholder="$ Enter an amount">
        </form>
        <div class="btnContainer">
          <a class="btn-primary" id="nextButton1" href="#">Next &rsaquo;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="setup2 hidden">
        <h4><br>Piggy will help you save money for the things that matter to you.</h4>
        <hr>
        <h3>Step 2: Tell us about your goal.</h3>
        <form>
          <p>What are you saving up for?</p>
            <input type="text" id="goalName" name="goalName" placeholder="Name your goal">
            <br><br>
          <p>How much will it cost?</p>
            <input type="number" id="goalAmount" name="goalAmount" placeholder="$ Enter an amount">
            <br><br>
          <p>When do you need to finish saving by?</p>
            <input type="text" id="date" name="goalDate" placeholder="Date">
        </form>
        <div class="btnContainer">
          <a class="btn-primary" id='backButton2' href='#'>&lsaquo; Back</a>
          <a class="btn-primary" id='nextButton2' href='#'>Next &rsaquo;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="setup3 hidden">
        <h3>Review your saving goal &amp; financial information:</h3>
        <hr>
        <h4 class="goalDescription"></h4>
        <h4 class="monthlyDescription"></h4>
        <h4 class="monthlyBudget"></h4>

        <hr>
        <h3>Your Saving Plan</h3>
        <h4 class="newBudget"></h4>
        <br>
        <h4 class="savingsDescription" style="font-weight: bold"></h4>
        <hr>

        <div class="btnContainer">
          <a class="btn-primary" id='backButton3' href='#'>&lsaquo; Back</a>
          <a class="btn-primary" id='confirm' href='#'>Confirm &rsaquo;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="setup4 hidden">
        <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
        <h3>You just finished setting your saving goal:</h3>
        <h4 class="goalDescription"></h4>
        <h4 class="newBudget"></h4>
        <h4 class="savingsDescription"></h4>
        <hr>
        <h4>If you meet your saving goal every week, you will earn Piggy Coins! You can use Piggy Coins to buy items for your Piggy avatar.</h4>
        <hr>
        <h3>Let's meet your new friend, Piggy Jr!</h3>
        <div class="btnContainer">
          <a class="btn-primary" id='finishButton' href='/dashboard'>Finish</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/setup.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
